## Welcome!

led-o-matic is arduino based device for controling of RGB LED stripe from android mobile phone over internet.

led-o-matic is open source and open hardware project using folowing technologies:

* arduino
* android
* python
* RESTfull web services   

[server](server.html) is running on Google app engine.

![Super image](img/ledomatic.jpg)


The initial work with the the systme almost completely working was written by geeks [team](team.html) on google developer days boot camp in Munich, Germany in November.

